<br>
When i was about 5 i said something like  &quot;I still am an apprentice&quot;<br>
<br>
When I reached 8/9 I said &quot;I've been thinking about the consequences of death more each day&quot;<br>
<br>
When I hit 11 I said &quot;I am seasoned enough to fear death&quot;<br>
<br>
When I was about 15 I said &quot;I am old enogh to fear death but it's still a lot of training necessary to become useful for the wayfarers brotherhood&quot;<br>
<br>
When I hit 20 I said &quot;I'm just experienced enough to do some work for the wayfarers brotherhood&quot;<br>
<br>
And what where the reactions?<br>
<br>
&quot;lvl and class&quot; (for the second time)<br>
the others turn round and run away/ignore me<br>
call me a stupid bitch/kid/wiseass<br>
<br>
so much for my roleplaying expirience on FV...<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=snoutfv>Snout FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 411<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/13/04 1:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=363.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: disagree</span><hr size=1> Yeah, I feel your pain about the level questions. I gave up trying to use RP in groups...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>I'm on my 40th page of my prayer book</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> has gone to: 40m<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>I am ready to meet the enemy</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is: rdy<br>
<br>
I<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em> need to rest a couple of minutes /e closes his eyes</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is: afk 2 min, k<br>
<br>
etc., etc.<br>
<br>
Now, I am not saying that RP is gone, but for the most part people are just lazy with it (myself included). <br>
<br>
In the end, RP is what you make of it. I don't think it is a bad as people think. I will say about half or more of the people I encounter will say OOC stuff either in brackets or between ~ ooc talk ~ , etc. To me, that is at least they acknowledge they are on an RP server.<br>
<br>
My final observation: I have been over 50+ level for a year and a half or so, so I can't comment on the lower levels, but I do notice more RP amongst higher level characters. *shrug* But I have nothing to base that on other than my observations and my own social interactions in game.<br>
<br>
Well, good luck and take care. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
