Feneant (who doesn't really roleplay but hates the other servers...) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=savriel>Savriel</A></span><br> Posts: 107<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/16/04 10:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm42.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=363.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lack of extremes</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Lots of terrific RP still on the server...good, evil, and of course the Iksar empire which defies either categorization...<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
